covery and supporting each other. They expressed gratitude for fan support during this challenging time. Ridgway detailed the medical considerations that influenced their choice.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtuber-jesse-ridgway-says-he-and-wife-made-difficult-choice-after-fetal-down-syndrome-diagnosis/articleshow/131516522.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/youtuber-jesse-ridgway-says-he-and-wife-made-difficult-choice-after-fetal-down-syndrome-diagnosis/articleshow/131516522.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-05T01:30:01+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131516515,imgsize-1014269.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Ex-wife of a Dubai prince 'abducted' amid bitter custody battle, lawyer raises alarm: 'She just vanished']]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131516215.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ex-wife-of-a-dubai-prince-3-children-abducted-amid-bitter-custody-battle-lawyer-raises-alarm-she-just-vanished/articleshow/131516215.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/ex-wife-of-a-dubai-prince-3-children-abducted-amid-bitter-custody-battle-lawyer-raises-alarm-she-just-vanished/articleshow/131516215.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-05T01:02:46+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131516243,imgsize-29780.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[4.5-inch stab to the neck: Drunk man jailed over fatal attack on Saudi student in England]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="