rder="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131513053.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Russian President Putin reassured that India's growing US ties won't harm its long-standing relationship with Russia. He dismissed attempts to pressure New Delhi, highlighting India's robust economic growth and predicting a significant expansion in bilateral trade, aiming for $100 billion in the coming years. Putin expressed confidence in continued strong economic engagement.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/useless-to-try-to-pressurise-pm-modi-putin-says-india-us-ties-wont-affect-india-russia-relations-praises-growth/articleshow/131513053.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/rest-of-world/useless-to-try-to-pressurise-pm-modi-putin-says-india-us-ties-wont-affect-india-russia-relations-praises-growth/articleshow/131513053.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T23:01:07+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131513084,imgsize-738508.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Miami real estate agent, ex-partner and two daughters found dead in murder-suicide]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131510898.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/miami-real-estate-agent-ex-partner-and-two-daughters-found-dead-in-murder-suicide-were-in-toxic-relationship-for-years/articleshow/131510898.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/miami-real-estate-agent-ex-partner-and-two-daughters-found-dead-in-murder-suicide-were-in-toxic-relationship-for-years/articleshow/131510898.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T22:49:10+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131512847,imgsize-69444.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[US lawmakers defy Trump in voting to end Iran war]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131512613.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Republican lawmakers are showing rare signs of independent thought, voting against President Trump's priorities on Capitol Hill. Recent acts of rebellion include opposing the Iran war without congressional authorization and blocking a controversial fund for alleged Biden administration overreach. While Trump's grip on the GOP remains strong, these small but noticeable tremors suggest a shift in congressional dynamics.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-defy-trump-in-voting-to-end-iran-war-plan-to-deny-him-funds-for-maga-insurrectionists/articleshow/131512613.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us/us-lawmakers-defy-trump-in-voting-to-end-iran-war-plan-to-deny-him-funds-for-maga-insurrectionists/articleshow/131512613.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-04T22:44:40+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Chidanand Rajghatta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131512708,imgsize-795283.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Sherpa survives 6-day Everest ordeal, crawls down 12km from 25k feet sans food, oxygen]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131512206.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/south-asia/sherpa-survives-6-day-everest-ordeal-crawls-down-12km-from-25k-feet-sans-food-oxygen/articleshow/131512206.cms]]